{"tid":2098010,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國移民局最新規定 留學生秋季如只接受網上教學就必須離開","createTime":"2020-07-07T07:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T01:15:15.000Z","uid":254371,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f16e90671ed0a56ea7bd3c70fc735f4bc01742f8","tid":2098010,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:38:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">美國移民和海關執法局發布與外國學生秋季入學有關的規定</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n美國移民和海關執法局發布了最新消息，關於外國學生如何在今年球季進入美國大學註冊，並同時保持他們的簽證身份，這為製定學術計劃的學校和學生提供了一些清晰的信息，也可能帶來許多令人頭疼的問題。<br />\n<br />\n支那留學生快d死返支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4d9b246175faf17fdb1cfe65faeb4f5cb74619","tid":2098010,"uid":254371,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:39:56.000Z","msg":"美國移民和海關執法局(Immigration and Customs Enforcement, 簡稱ICE)發布了人們熱切期待的最新消息，內容是關於外國學生如何在今年球季進入美國大學註冊，同時保持他們的簽證身份，這為製定學術計劃的學校和學生提供了一些清晰的信息，也可能帶來許多令人頭疼的問題。<br />\n<br />\nICE的學生和交流訪問學者項目(Student and Exchange Visitor Program)週一發布的指導意見取決於學校是完全網上授課，還是現場授課，抑或兩者兼而有之。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca1ee66a99d9df98350b7f8db8abd0a049b1924","tid":2098010,"uid":131282,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:40:33.000Z","msg":"敖狗咁你點算？洗唔洗返香港？"},{"pid":"93091026219f2b052e3c6c8c6f86b49719a55a70","tid":2098010,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ca1ee66a99d9df98350b7f8db8abd0a049b1924","tid":2098010,"uid":131282,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:40:33.000Z","msg":"敖狗咁你點算？洗唔洗返香港？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"一早已經係美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2e906b80933259931556b353348c735459540a","tid":2098010,"uid":254371,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T07:48:18.000Z","msg":"以前係大學好撚憎班支那留學生<br />\n又蠢又成日free rider <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3dbebc46b9978529871fe44d68bc3357d24b202","tid":2098010,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571d0eb3ccbcbc30d4f0928d9ebd4e79cff8c19e","tid":2098010,"uid":21592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:21:02.000Z","msg":"番左大陸可能無得再番美國，要搞內循環<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e99f002ec6e8bfe644f365e5c589e0702890299","tid":2098010,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:01:16.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf2d6f6ad3b293785f2da925bd150f96d5b7643","tid":2098010,"uid":254371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e263757359bfb6ac2cef855c941b0a09466869","tid":2098010,"uid":8880,"